snippet.title: Turbo Leaper SAGE '23 Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Submission for the SAGE' 23 trailer.

Turbo Leaper is an upcoming platformer game!  The multiverse is in disarray; play as multiple characters, such as the special guest Scruffy from Super Freaks!  There will be a demo releasing for the SAGE 2023 event.

Extradimensional Portalhopping OST by Zane Little.
Turbo Leaper game and original characters by Riegelsoft.
Super Freaks by SuperFreaksDev/KingNormal.
